OL,3,GWales
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FIt will be a dry day across the
OL,6,Fcountry with early patches of low
OL,7,Fcloud and fog lifting during the
OL,8,Fmorning to leave plenty of sunshine.
OL,9,FFeeling pleasantly warm in the
OL,10,Fafternoon in the gentle mainly
OL,11,Fnortherly wind.
OL,12,
OL,13,CTonight:FIt will remain dry during the
OL,14,Fevening and overnight. There will be
OL,15,Fclear spells, although some low cloud
OL,16,Fis likely to reform, along with a few
OL,17,Fmist or fog patches.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
